cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper focuses on visual recognition and image data collection, which are key topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of webly supervised learning also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) techniques. The paper also discusses the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) to extract visual concepts from text. Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed approach using machine learning techniques (cs.LG).
